noise = 1e-6;
                        channel_noise = (1-noise) * channel + noise * channel;
                        for party=1:nrparties
                            for x=1:ins(party)
                                for a=1:outs(party)
                                    POVMs{party}{x}{a} = (1-noise) * POVMs{party}{x}{a} + noise * POVMs{party}{x}{a};
                                end
                            end
                        end

                        channel_noise = (1-noise) * channel + noise * channel;
                        for party=1:nrparties
                            for x=1:ins(party)

                        noise = 1e-6;
                        channel_noise = (1-noise) * channel + noise * channel;
                        for party=1:nrparties
                            for x=1:ins(party)
                                for a=1:outs(party)
                                    POVMs{party}{x}{a} = (1-noise) * POVMs{party}{x}{a} + noise * POVMs{party}{x}{a};
                                end
                            end
